import React from 'react'
import {
    Button,
    Flex,
    Heading,
    Stack,
    Spacer,
    Text,
    Image,
    InputLeftElement,
    FormControl,
    Box,
    InputGroup,
    Icon,
    Grid,
    GridItem,
    FormLabel,
    Progress,
    Input,
    Textarea
} from "@chakra-ui/react";
import { Checkbox, CheckboxGroup } from "@chakra-ui/react";

const Welcome = () => {
    return (
        <Flex  bg="#F9F9F9" direction="column" justify="center" align="center">
            <Flex  direction="column" justify="center" w="80%" align="center">
            <Heading mt="80px" mb="45px">
                Welcome back
            </Heading>
            <Input
              height="64px" 
              border="none" 
              color="#141414" 
              borderBottom="1px solid #141414" 
              placeholder="Email Address" 
              mb="24px"/>
            
            </Flex>
            

        </Flex>
    )
}

export default Welcome
